result.name: Safe-Bubble & Malt

reviews.text:
Amazing whisky & champagne selection in hidden cozy bar where the service goes above and beyond.
Ron at the bar is a cocktail wizard and extremely passionate and knowledgeable about anything you can purchase in the bar.
Highly recommended!

Under the radar must of a whiskey bar. Mind-blowing selection of whiskies - largest in Hong Kong. Ron, the bartender, a shining example of how all bartenders should be. Professional, discreet, unassuming, efficient,  friendly, knowledgeable...

Huge selection of whiskeys.  Some very unique and rare finds.  Quiet place.  Not a huge bar but good for couples and small groups.  
Definitely not cheap.

Great discovery. the bar is hidden from outside, as the name can tell, the entrance looks like a safe so be careful not to miss it while walking around Queen's road. Inside,you will be surprised by the amount of whiskeys that are available: bottles range from the 80s to more recent ones and brand variety is wide, satisfying first timers and whisky lovers. I had run instead, Jamaican and Caribbean, which turned out to be very tasty. Reccomended for a cozy night (space is small) with friends. Staff is welcoming and helpful, which makes the stay even more pleasant. If you like malts and spirits, stop by and try out to judge by yourself. Also in the area lots of places for food if on munchies
Great ambience and service
